Text: "Sri lanaka is a wonderful paradise with magnificent views and colourful culture.and\
  \ a heaven for spicy foods.\n\nThere are blue skies which always good whether to\
  \ travel around the country. You can travel any corner of the sri lanka with in\
  \ one day with minimum budget LKR 500 that is a very good opportunity for you to\
  \ enjoy the sceneic beauty in sri lanka\n\nAnd the people are very nice to meet\
  \ and with great hospitatlity.\nDont forget to taste king coconut when you visit\
  \ sri lanka which always makes your thirsty away.\n\nThere are beautiful sandy beaches\
  \ around the island and if you need to enjoy wild life you can visit yala, udawalawa\
  \ ,kumana jungle . Again if you boring with wild life then you can enjoy the nice\
  \ cold climate in hill country kandy ,ella and nuwara eliya. Dont forget to take\
  \ the train ride when you visit hill country that will be the one of the most beutiful\
  \ train ride you will ever enjoy.\n\nSri lanaka having good and nice their own food\
  \ culture. And plus it not too expensive \n\nSri lanka is one of a paradise you\
  \ must visit in your life time.enjoy travelling"
